Release Notes
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
0.01 - collect_data.py will connect with the twitter api useing a hardcoded
user name and password.  The twitter streaming api is dumped straight to the
terminal.  The data base initialization is written but not yet tested in any
way.




Database Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This description is tentative and WILL change as I compact the database and
data redundency.  I have much more research to do, but I may even switch to 
redis noSQL.

+------------------------+
| Tables_in_twitter_test |
+------------------------+
| tv_places              |
| tv_tweets              |
| tv_users               |
+------------------------+

This table holds the information pertaining to a single tweet.
Redundant information about users and places are stored in
tv_users and tv_places respectively
+-------------------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field                   | Type         | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+-------------------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| tweet_id                | bigint(20)   | NO   | PRI | NULL    |       |
| created_at              | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| text                    | varchar(150) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| source                  | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| favorited               | bit(1)       | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| truncated               | bit(1)       | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| retweeted               | bit(1)       | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| retweet_count           | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| in_reply_to_user_id     | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| in_reply_to_status_id   | mediumtext   | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| in_reply_to_screen_name | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| in_reply_to_user_id_str | mediumtext   | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| in_reply_to_id_str      | mediumtext   | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| id_str                  | mediumtext   | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| geo_type                | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| lat                     | float        | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| lon                     | float        | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| user_id                 | int(11)      | YES  | MUL | NULL    |       |
| place_id                | bigint(20)   | YES  | MUL | NULL    |       |
+-------------------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+


+------------------------------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field                              | Type         | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+------------------------------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| user_id                            | bigint(20)   | NO   | PRI | NULL    |       |
| user_flags                         | bit(10)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| favorites_count                    | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| friends_count                      | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| listed_count                       | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| utc_offset                         | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| statuses_count                     | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| followers_count                    | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_image_url_https            | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_image_url                  | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_background_image_url_https | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_background_image_url       | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_sidebar_fill_color         | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_text_color                 | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_link_color                 | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_background_color           | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| id_str                             | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| created_at                         | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| time_zone                          | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| profile_sidebar_border_color       | int(11)      | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| screen_name                        | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| url                                | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| description                        | varchar(512) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| lang                               | varchar(24)  | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| place                              | int(11)      | YES  | MUL | NULL    |       |
+------------------------------------+--------------+------+-----+---------+-------+


+--------------+-----------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| Field        | Type            | Null | Key | Default | Extra |
+--------------+-----------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
| place_id     | bigint(20)      | NO   | PRI | NULL    |       |
| name         | varchar(32)     | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| url          | varchar(512)    | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| country      | varchar(32)     | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| place_type   | varchar(32)     | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| country_code | char(2)         | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| full_name    | varchar(70)     | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| bounding_box | varbinary(128)  | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
| attributes   | varbinary(1024) | YES  |     | NULL    |       |
+--------------+-----------------+------+-----+---------+-------+
